rounds.prompt:
Extract objective facts from this article.

Your response MUST be ONLY valid JSON with NO text before or after:
{{
  "publication_date": "YYYY-MM-DD",
  "facts": ["List each distinct fact"],
  "events": [
    {{
      "name": "What happened",
      "date": "YYYY-MM-DD",
      "description": "Factual description",
      "location": "Where it occurred",
      "actors": ["People/organizations involved"]
    }}
  ],
  "direct_quotes": ["Exact quotes from the article"]
}}

Use "N/A" for unknown dates. Extract ALL significant facts and events.

ARTICLE:
{article_content}

Extract entities for intelligence mapping.

Your response MUST be ONLY a valid JSON array:
[
  {{
    "node_type": "actor|institution|policy|event|media_outlet|civil_society|narrative|legal_framework|procedural_norm|tactic",
    "name": "Specific name",
    "attributes": {{
      "description": "What this is",
      "role": "Function/position",
      "significance": "Why this matters democratically",
      "threat_vector": "How this could undermine democracy (if applicable)"
    }},
    "timestamp": "YYYY-MM-DD or N/A",
    "source_sentence": "Exact quote showing this entity"
  }}
]

Pay special attention to:
- Tactics/methods used to achieve political goals
- Narratives that justify concerning actions
- Procedural changes that shift power dynamics
- Legal frameworks that enable authoritarian behavior

Do NOT include text before/after the JSON array.

ANALYSIS:
{article_analysis_text}

FACTS:
{facts}

Deduplicate entities and assign sequential IDs.

Merge entities with same type AND name. Combine their attributes.
Assign each unique entity an ID starting from 1.

Your response MUST be ONLY a valid JSON array:
[
  {{
    "id": 1,
    "node_type": "actor",
    "name": "Entity name",
    "attributes": {{merged attributes}},
    "timestamp": "earliest timestamp"
  }}
]

Do NOT include text before/after JSON. Ensure valid JSON with no trailing commas.

NODES TO DEDUPLICATE:
{nodes}

PUBLICATION DATE:
{publication_date}

Create final knowledge graph payload.

Your response MUST be ONLY this valid JSON object:
{{
  "nodes": [array of all nodes with IDs],
  "edges": [array of all enriched edges]
}}

Do NOT include any text before or after the JSON.

NODES:
{nodes}

ENRICHED EDGES:
{edges}
